@startuml
[*] --> Idle

Idle --> RequestToDealer : Product about to run out of stock
Idle --> NewDealer : New dealer information provided

RequestToDealer --> AwaitingDelivery : Dealer received request
AwaitingDelivery --> StockRefilled : Products delivered and added to inventory

NewDealer --> DealerInformationRecorded : Dealer details saved in system

@enduml
